{"tid":449927,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺人大左學樂器真係好難","createTime":"2017-10-27T15:45:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-29T05:18:23.000Z","uid":66280,"like":6,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"5359af8992a818e4be68200d8d0f5adffa2df5ed","tid":449927,"uid":66280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T15:45:18.000Z","msg":"其實以前一路都好想學結他<br />\n但係中學嗰陣掛住打波同補習<br />\n根本冇時間學<br />\n自己又好鍾意唱歌<br />\n成日都想學結他可以自彈自唱自娛一下<br />\n<br />\n而家大左 有少少空餘時間想學果陣<br />\n覺得啲手指好唔靈活 又僵硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身自己節奏感唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗翻轉頭真係覺得自己當初好傻<br />\n唔堅持去學<br />\n<br />\n雖然連登唔知有幾多中學雞<br />\n不過都想同大家講句<br />\n趁有時間 隻手又靈活果陣去學下唔同樂器<br />\n音樂真係一個人生活必備嘅調劑品<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89910056e6128156c83e97a0e639714bb664e74b","tid":449927,"uid":1833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T15:47:37.000Z","msg":"呢樣真<br />\n巴打喺邊學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99eb935fbb5d9021c22927d362e62d80d21e6d3c","tid":449927,"uid":64227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T15:59:46.000Z","msg":"只係為咗自娛嘅話幾時學都得啦"},{"pid":"aeada38d4b08b490187295293774e113d793e3d2","tid":449927,"uid":57835,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T16:01:00.000Z","msg":"幾歲啊？五六十啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6adcea1fac949d769c67126ca244a6c73a0293b","tid":449927,"uid":128850,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T16:02:39.000Z","msg":"我老豆宜家44歲都走去學爵士鼓<br />\n一學就學咗半年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2c84356f37f9d17b359ab55931750e3e5e88ff0","tid":449927,"uid":80183,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T16:04:36.000Z","msg":"一定要用拍子機<br />\n唔好怕同懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ang